				<h1>Company Profile</h1>
				<p>Micro Materials (P) Ltd. is a materials science company. We focus on bringing innovative nano and micro technologies and materials catalysts to marketplace. The new generation catalysts are the result of a radically new proprietary process.</p>
				<p>Micro Materials (P) Ltd. has the exclusive commercialization and marketing rights for this technology from the Indian Institute of Science, Bangalore. The Institute is a leading research and teaching institution with over eight decades of outstanding contribution to the fields of science and engineering. The lead researcher, Prof. M.S.Hegde, is a renowned scientist. He has published many peer-reviewed papers in international scholarly journals. In addition, Micro Materials collaborates with renowned nanotechnology researchers from around the world.</p>
				<p>Micro Materials is interested in joining hands with leading corporations in commercializing the new generation of catalysts for multiple applications. Micro Materials will provide additional technical details and other supporting data to interested parties.			    </p>
